u can make informed decisions about releasing tax revenue and leveraging your investment to generate additional development.</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '215-revision-7', '', '', '2010-12-27 17:44:45', '2010-12-27 17:44:45', '', 215, 'http://dev.umbaugh.com/215-revision-7', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
