(277, 3, '2010-12-14 09:24:59', '2010-12-14 09:24:59', 'We love to share our expertise!  Umbaugh representatives frequently  speak before seminars, conferences and government hearings to help even  the experts stay current during these changing times for local  governments and finances.  You''ll find here presentations, timely  articles from past issues of Footnotes and even a white paper or two.   (Don''t let the term ''white paper'' scare you; it''s technical, but  understandable, information.)\r\n\r\nCheck this section often  we''ll update it constantly.\r\n\r\nIf you''d like to schedule a presentation tailored to  your group  or if you don''t find the topic you''re looking for, please  call us at (800 number) and we''ll find the person or information you''re  looking for.', 'Our Library', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '85-revision-4', '', '', '2010-12-14 09:24:59', '2010-12-14 09:24:59', '', 85, 'http://dev.umbaugh.com/85-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
