', 'Schools', 'At UMBAUGH, we don''t represent both sides of the table. We represent you as a school district. Our independence from the bond underwriting assures you of the greatest objectivity in analyzing, determining and planning - whether that''s for capital improvements or operating funds.\r\n<br /><br/>\r\nWe quickly respond to your needs. At public hearings, we calmly, accurately and professionally answer all the financial questions your constituents - and your board - will have.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '217-revision-6', '', '', '2011-01-04 16:30:30', '2011-01-04 16:30:30', '', 217, 'http://dev.umbaugh.com/217-revision-6', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
